&gt; &gt; sound such as the minibox as apposed to the super radio each
&gt; produce a distinctive sound.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; Lastly, if you are new to box research you may not have a permanent
&gt; tech/guide assigned yet and who ever is available
&gt; &gt; at the time of your session will take control of that session. I
&gt; find that your tech does not bother to seek out recognisable
&gt; &gt; noise fragments to form his or her message until you have developed
&gt; a working relationship as well as a personal one with them.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; There is no exact explanation for any of this, it is all conjecture
&gt; by the individual researcher but I try to answer any questions based
&gt; on my experience.
